title: To the Dark Room of Souls
description: The evil that has been trapped in the Moorehead houses walks free, seeking its revenge, and Emily, Adam and Jimmy must fight one last time for their lives.In order to defeat the black magic, they must trace it to its source, but the trail leads to the greatest evil of all. Are they strong enough to win the battle, or has their luck run out?The story of Moorehead Manor begins with book 1: Moorehead ManorThe saga of Moorehead Manor continues with book 2: In the House of the Vodouisant
author: David McMullen-Sullivan
